data.description: WELCOME HOME TO CANAVERAL GROVES! MOTIVATED SELLER! BRING ALL OFFERS! This Single Family Pool Home sits on a 1.02 Corner Acre Lot. This corner acre lot is High and Dry and easily accessible by a paved road! This home features 3 Bedrooms, 2 Bathrooms and a 2 Car Attached Garage, 2018 Shingle Asphalt Roof, 2022 Lennox HVAC System with a UV Germicidal System, FPL Certified Electrical Panel, 2019 Whirlpool Water Heater, Stainless Steel Appliances, New Bathroom Fixtures, Planation Shutters, Tile and Vinyl Laminate Flooring, Indoor Laundry. Freshly Painted Interior and Exterior with Beautiful Landscaping! Outdoor features include an In-ground Fiberglass Pool with a Spill over Spa, Vinyl Fence Surrounding Pool Area, screened Lanai and sitting area that is Perfect for outdoor entertaining!
